            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#minskiJ" start="4177.368" end="x">I cannot remember for sure. First of all, the housing conditions were terrible. There was . . . They have selected for the <a class="placename" href="#vothC65" type="camp">Lodz Ghetto</a> the worst . . . the worst section of <a class="placename" href="#vothL82">Lodz</a>; that is, where the worst skum had lived before. Those were mostly broken down dwellings; and people [in the Ghetto] lived under the most frightful conditions. At times the people lived ten families in one flat. You can imagine what the results were under these most horrible hygienic conditions.</span>
