            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#minskiJ" start="4655.038" end="x">And so we found ourselves on the march; and unfortunately a great number of our prisoners were shot down, especially by the Ukrainian <a class="term" href="#vothG_ss">SS</a> who hardly spoke a word of German . . .</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
