    </p>
    <div id="map_vothC86" style="width: 250px; height: 250px;"></div>
                        <p class="placename">
                Oranienburg
            </p>
                            <p class="subcamp_of">
                <strong>Subcamp of: </strong>
                Sachsenhausen
            </p>
                            <p class="municipality">
                <strong>Location:</strong>
                Oranienburg, Germany<br />
                            </p>
                            <div>
                Established by the Nazis as one of their first detention facilities (1933) to hold political opponents from the Berlin region. It was eventually replaced in the area by Sachsenhausen concentration camp (1936).
            </div>
                            <style type="text/css">
